description: An alien creature stands on a rocky landscape under a starry sky, pointing towards a fleet of large, disc-shaped spacecraft. Below it, a USA Explorer II rover with multiple wheels and a prominent antenna surveys the ground. The alien appears agitated, shouting towards the rover, creating an ironic scenario where a human exploration vehicle designed to search for extraterrestrial life is present on a world where an alien already exists and is preoccupied with a different group of alien visitors. The absurdity is heightened by the alien seemingly directing the rover to locate the incoming spacecraft.
caption: "FIND THEM!"
